00:32.375 --> 00:34.375
(ROCKET SNORING)

00:37.833 --> 00:38.916
(GRUNTS)

00:41.291 --> 00:42.500
(GRUNTS)

00:45.333 --> 00:47.166
(SHOWER RUNNING)

00:56.500 --> 00:57.625
(GRUNTS)

01:00.500 --> 01:01.583
Whee!

01:08.166 --> 01:09.166
(GRUNTS)

01:12.916 --> 01:14.333
-(BONES CRACK)
-(GRUNTS)

01:39.583 --> 01:40.791
(BEEPS)

01:40.875 --> 01:42.291
-(GRUNTS)
-(EXPLOSION)

01:45.500 --> 01:46.916
(CHUCKLING)

01:48.583 --> 01:49.791
(GRUNTS)

01:49.875 --> 01:50.958
(YELPS)

01:57.416 --> 01:58.416
(GRUNTS)

01:59.291 --> 02:01.125
(ALARM BEEPING)

02:01.500 --> 02:02.916
(HUMMING)

02:06.375 --> 02:07.791
ROCKET: Groot, where... (GASPS)

02:08.416 --> 02:10.750
Groot, are you okay?
Groot, are you dead?

02:10.833 --> 02:14.375
Oh, yeah, you're right there with the...
Wait. Are those these ship's fuel rods?

02:15.416 --> 02:17.666
Wait, how did you get the walls wet
and on fire?

02:17.750 --> 02:19.916
Wait, what's that? (SNIFFING)

02:20.000 --> 02:22.250
Is that Drax's soap?

02:22.333 --> 02:25.333
He's been lookin' everywhere for this.
He won't shut up about it.

02:25.416 --> 02:28.541
Groot, why does it look like
a bomb went off in here?

02:29.833 --> 02:31.083
I am Groot.

02:31.166 --> 02:32.833
A bomb did go off?

02:32.916 --> 02:34.875
What? How did you get... Hey!

02:34.958 --> 02:36.000
Don't give me that look.

02:36.083 --> 02:38.416
Don't think you're getting out of this
by being cute.

02:38.500 --> 02:41.166
Why are you handing me this?
What is this? More trash?

02:41.916 --> 02:44.375
It better be a written apology.
Let's see this.

02:45.333 --> 02:46.333
Oh.

02:46.416 --> 02:47.916
Oh, look how big you are.

02:48.000 --> 02:49.375
Oh, this is very nice.

02:49.875 --> 02:51.333
We gotta get this framed.

02:51.416 --> 02:53.458
Put up on the top of the fridge.

02:54.000 --> 02:56.416
I can't stay mad at you, can I?

02:57.333 --> 02:58.750
(MUSIC CONTINUES)

02:58.833 --> 03:01.666
-What is that? Is that my tail hair?
-(EXPLOSION)

03:02.583 --> 03:04.833
Groot! (GRUNTING)

03:04.916 --> 03:06.083
You gotta be kidding me.
